Package: LSBP
Type: Package
Title: Tractable Bayesian density regression via logit stick-breaking priors
Version: 0.0.4
Date: 2020-06-21
Author: Tommaso Rigon
Maintainer: Tommaso Rigon <tommaso.rigon@gmail.com>
Description: Posterior inference for the logit stick-breaking model with Gaussian kernels. The LSBP package is an implementation of the algorithms described in the paper: Rigon, T. and Durante, D. (2020). Tractable Bayesian Tractable Bayesian density regression via logit stick-breaking priors. Journal of Statistical Planning and Inference.
